data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bed (1 non conforming) 2 bath, with a  2 car garage! Step into the open living area, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. Enjoy the privacy of a split bedroom floor plan offering tranquility and space for everyone. The kitchen boasts newer appliances and hardware making meal preparation a breeze. Take in the stunning views all from the comfort of your own home. Plus, with all new electrical outlets, convenience meets modern living. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your new home!
